{"tid":1386793,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣請注意修辭","createTime":"2019-07-30T11:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T15:00:28.000Z","uid":276716,"like":130,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"89e2d98f2a9385ee9de92429f047cfdda910cf1e","tid":1386793,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:56:22.000Z","msg":"小弟有幾個建議。文宣修辭非常重要。<br />\n<br />\nV 市民<br />\nX 示威者<br />\n<br />\n冇編號/委任証嘅警察<br />\nV 身穿警察制服的武裝人員<br />\nX 警察<br />\n<br />\n有編號/委任証嘅警察<br />\nV 特區政府警察<br />\nX 警察<br />\n<br />\nV 被武裝人員挾走<br />\nX 被拘捕"},{"pid":"97ba78c73620d30a70210a0696980bb2ab70e9c2","tid":1386793,"uid":276716,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:58:58.000Z","msg":"V 發射催淚彈<br />\nX 施放催淚彈<br />\n<br />\nV 衝擊/襲擊市民<br />\nX 驅散示威者<br />\n<br />\nV 強搶物資<br />\nX 沒收物資<br />\n<br />\n未有搜查令及業主同意下進入私人物業<br />\nV 闖入<br />\nX 進入<br />\n<br />\nV 展示恐嚇標語<br />\nX 舉黑旗示警<br />\n<br />\n例句<br />\n<br />\nV 展示恐嚇標語後，身穿警察制服的武裝部隊發射催淚彈襲擊市民。<br />\nX 舉黑旗示警無效後，警察施放催淚彈驅散示威者。<br />\n<br />\nV 身穿警察制服的武裝部隊闖入商場內，挾走多名市民。<br />\n❎警察進入商場內，拘捕多名示威者。"},{"pid":"2170649fa03bfbcecf80f091304d6095655a48d9","tid":1386793,"uid":191867,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:46:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用啱字真係可以改變成件事嘅觀感，唔可以俾對家帶風向"},{"pid":"8a675a7bd3a251195676a68f0c919d746e6a7d41","tid":1386793,"uid":295481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:47:34.000Z","msg":"香港加油<br />\n<br />\n5/8 九巴不合作運動 正式啟動！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390913\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390913</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a65a41f8dcc8b80817e5e56ce555e244c48a1b97","tid":1386793,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:16:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"59f9d78c71ca9f35824e8ca21fe09052deb8fa3e","tid":1386793,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime